"""Triton kernel for gather_and_maybe_dequant_cache.

Gathers tokens from paged KV cache into a contiguous destination buffer,
optionally dequantizing FP8 data to BF16. Designed to replace the vLLM
CUDA kernel for MLA attention (DeepSeekV2/V4).

Supported entry sizes:
  - 576 (kv_lora_rank=512 + qk_rope_head_dim=64) for DeepSeekV4
  - 320 (kv_lora_rank=256 + qk_rope_head_dim=64) for DeepSeekV2
"""

